{"tid":2447493,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"由這一分鐘我一生就只有您　明日縱使不堪　基本法永續不放棄","createTime":"2021-03-15T08:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T14:19:36.000Z","uid":38189,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d32da3c293b079909d24fcd38eec4eb0180e879","tid":2447493,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"逐晚倒數望四眼準備 願您快點又再去選舉<br />\n寂寥足足幾個月 從面書減少距離<br />\n而偏偏竟不知怎說起 <br />\n<br />\n是太想念你 先會看熱時<br />\n只想可加入您 然後撐您 讓您驚喜<br />\n由這一分鐘我選舉就只撐您<br />\n明日縱使不堪 阻不到我用心愛您 <br />\n<br />\n讓我一生當熱民 洋達您比生死重要<br />\n連話語 也沒法盛載得起 <br />\n<br />\nI'll give my life to be near you with passion prime <br />\nFor I have nothing left to kejin I love passion times <br />\n<br />\n願意一生當熱民 這改變因您<br />\n承諾我會永遠保護您 <br />\n<br />\n逐秒擴張 熱血嘅土地<br />\n合上眼睛像與您一起 <br />\n<br />\n為何左膠於遍地<br />\n和熱狗總打對台<br />\n雲根哥 都不知怎說起 <br />\n<br />\n是太想念您 先會課熱時<br />\n一生想感謝您 承諾撐您 讓您當選<br />\n由這一分鐘我一生就只有您<br />\n明日縱使不堪 基本法永續不放棄<br />\n讓我忠於這熱民 皇上您比生死重要<br />\n連話語也沒法盛載得起 <br />\n<br />\nI'll give my life to be near you with passion prime <br />\nFor I have nothing left to kejin I love passion times <br />\n<br />\n讓我終於不動搖 這改變因您<br />\n如若您欠信我的力氣 <br />\n<br />\n我唱這首歌 為您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9c60ffe88403884507b90e135dd2bdf866b8ae","tid":2447493,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0100353329e053c7581a2be6dd5acc000cb82e","tid":2447493,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2fec74ba454915612b